OL,3,CHarry Styles fans warned about hot
OL,4,Cweather before Wembley Stadium show
OL,6,FHarry Styles fans have been warned to
OL,7,Fstay hydrated and wear loose and
OL,8,Fbreathable clothing to his gig at
OL,9,FWembley Stadium on Tuesday.
OL,11,FThe One Direction star will take to
OL,12,Fthe stage amid scorching temperatures
OL,13,Fin the UK.
OL,15,FIt is forecast to be 33C in Wembley at
OL,16,F5pm when the doors to the concert open
OL,17,Fand fans have been instructed not to
OL,18,Farrive too early to avoid waiting
OL,19,Foutside in the sun.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
