OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782301688
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans warned about hot
OL,4,Cweather before Wembley Stadium show
OL,6,FThere will be little relief from the
OL,7,Fheat during the support set from
OL,8,Fcountry star Shania Twain and will
OL,9,Fstill be 31C when Styles takes to the
OL,10,Fstage at 8.15pm.
OL,12,FGuests have also been told that metal
OL,13,For hard plastic water bottles will be
OL,14,Fallowed inside the stadium, in a break
OL,15,Ffrom usual venue rules.
OL,17,FThese can then be filled at one of the
OL,18,Ffree refillable water stations located
OL,19,Finside.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
