OL,3,CHarry Styles fans warned about hot
OL,4,Cweather before Wembley Stadium show
OL,6,FMeanwhile, bottled water sold across
OL,7,Fall bars will have a 50% reduction in
OL,8,Fprice.
OL,10,FA message from the stadium to all
OL,11,Fguests attending the show also urges
OL,12,Fthem to take regular breaks in shaded
OL,13,Fareas and to wear sun cream.
OL,15,FFree sun cream will be available from
OL,16,Fall information points inside the
OL,17,Fstadium.
OL,19,FFans are also advised to avoid
OL,20,Fconsuming too much alcohol and instead
OL,21,Fstay hydrated with water.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
