OL,3,CHarry Styles fans warned about hot
OL,4,Cweather before Wembley Stadium show
OL,6,FThey are also asked to adhere to the
OL,7,Fadvice on screens and information
OL,8,Fpoints around the stadium.
OL,10,FTuesday's show will be the sixth of a
OL,11,F12-night residency at the London venue
OL,12,F` a bid to beat Coldplay's record of
OL,13,F10 performances there last year.
OL,15,FThe string of shows is poised to smash
OL,16,Fthe record for the most performances
OL,17,Fby any artist in a single year at the
OL,18,Fnational stadium.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
