OL,3,CHarry Styles fans warned about hot
OL,4,Cweather before Wembley Stadium show
OL,6,FStyles will also beat pop superstar
OL,7,FTaylor Swift's record for the most
OL,8,Fconcerts performed at Wembley by a
OL,9,Fsolo artist during a single concert
OL,10,Frun.
OL,12,FShe performed eight shows at the venue
OL,13,Fas part of the Eras Tour in 2024.
OL,15,FStyles will perform his final show at
OL,16,FWembley on July 4.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
